(4.1 System Architecture) Tj
T*
(- Architecture style: React SPA + Supabase BaaS.) Tj
T*
(- UI Layer: Pages and layouts for student/admin roles.) Tj
T*
(- Service Layer: notesService, groupsService, messagesService, usersService,) Tj
T*
(  complaintsService, analyticsService, leaderboardService, storageService.) Tj
T*
(- Data Layer: Supabase Postgres tables, Storage buckets, and Realtime channels.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.2 Database Design and Entity-Relationship Model) Tj
T*
(Primary tables:) Tj
T*
(- profiles \(extends auth.users\)) Tj
T*
(- notes) Tj
T*
(- groups) Tj
T*
(- group_members) Tj
T*
(- messages) Tj
T*
(- complaints) Tj
T*
(- leaderboard_points) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(ER summary:) Tj
T*
(- auth.users \(1\) -> profiles \(1\)) Tj
T*
(- profiles \(1\) -> notes \(M\)) Tj
T*
(- profiles \(1\) -> complaints \(M\)) Tj
T*
(- groups \(1\) -> group_members \(M\)) Tj
T*
(- groups \(1\) -> messages \(M\)) Tj
T*
(- profiles \(1\) -> group_members \(M\)) Tj
T*
(- profiles \(1\) -> messages \(M\)) Tj
T*
(- profiles \(1\) -> leaderboard_points \(M\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.3 Data Flow Diagrams) Tj
T*
(Level 0:) Tj
T*
(- User -> React App -> Supabase -> Database/Storage) Tj
T*
(- Realtime events flow from Supabase back to app screens.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Level 1 major flows:) Tj
T*
(- Authentication flow: login/signup -> session -> profile fetch -> role routing.) Tj
T*
(- Note flow: upload file -> storage path -> note row -> notes list/dashboard.) Tj
T*
(- Chat flow: send message -> messages table -> realtime subscription update.) Tj
T*
(- Complaint flow: create complaint -> admin updates -> realtime status refresh.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.4 Use Case Diagrams and Descriptions) Tj
T*
(Actors:) Tj
T*
(- Student) Tj
T*
(- Admin) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Key use cases:) Tj
T*
(- UC-01 Signup/Login) Tj
T*
(- UC-02 Upload Note) Tj
T*
(- UC-03 Join Group) Tj
T*
(- UC-04 Send Message) Tj
T*
(- UC-05 Submit Complaint) Tj
T*
(- UC-06 Moderate Note) Tj
T*
(- UC-07 Manage Users) Tj
T*
(- UC-08 View Analytics) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4.5 Module-Level Design) Tj
T*
(- Auth Module: AuthContext + Supabase Auth.) Tj
T*
(- Routing Module: AppRouter + ProtectedRoute.) Tj
T*
(- Notes Module: listing, upload, moderation.) Tj
ET
endstream
