(Chapter 5 - Implementation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.1 Development Environment Setup) Tj
T*
(- Install Node.js LTS.) Tj
T*
(- Run: npm install) Tj
T*
(- Configure .env with VITE_SUPABASE_URL and VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY.) Tj
T*
(- Run: npm run dev) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.2 Database Schema Implementation) Tj
T*
(- Execute supabase_setup.sql once in Supabase SQL Editor.) Tj
T*
(- Script includes: table creation, indexes, triggers, RLS policies,) Tj
T*
(  storage buckets, and realtime publication updates.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.3 Authentication Module) Tj
T*
(- Signup/login/logout implemented via Supabase Auth in AuthContext.) Tj
T*
(- Profile fetched from public.profiles and mapped to app-level user object.) Tj
T*
(- ProtectedRoute enforces role-based route access.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.4 Note Upload Module) Tj
T*
(- NotesPage form collects metadata and file.) Tj
T*
(- notesService.uploadNote uploads file to notes-files bucket,) Tj
T*
(  then inserts metadata into notes table.) Tj
T*
(- Trigger awards points for note upload.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.5 Peer Review and Rating Module) Tj
T*
(- Current code includes rating display placeholders in NotesPage.) Tj
T*
(- notesService currently sets rating values as placeholders.) Tj
T*
(- Sorting by "rating" currently proxies to downloads.) Tj
T*
(- Full rating persistence can be added with a note_ratings table.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.6 Filtering and Sorting Engine) Tj
T*
(- Server-side filtering by subject/search using Supabase query methods.) Tj
T*
(- Debounced client search input reduces repeated calls.) Tj
T*
(- Sorting supports recent and downloads.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5.7 Dashboard and Profile Module) Tj
T*
(- Student Dashboard: top notes, leaderboard snapshot, quick actions.) Tj
T*
(- Admin Dashboard: KPI cards, trends, complaints summary.) Tj
T*
(- Profile page: update full name/about/avatar and preference controls.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Chapter 6 - Testing) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6.1 Testing Strategy) Tj
T*
(- Prioritize critical user journeys: auth, upload, moderation, complaints, realtime chat.) Tj
T*
(- Validate both role logic and backend RLS behavior.) Tj
ET
